item.title: How do i set my client online!?
item.dc:creator: @Dharma Dharma
item.description:
@Dharma wrote:

Make sure you got a no-ip and you put it in your client.
You login w/ 127.0.0.1 and your buddy logs in w/ your no-ip
Also you need to portforward which isn’t hard unless you have a weird network system set up like me…
Go to portforward.com
